{"id": "1506738574861799474", "channel_id": "1506738574861799474", "author_id": "735137568307282011", "author_name": "reya.li", "content": "I was playing a challenge run on stream today and it also made me realize that with no material event running at all, there is no way for brand new players (who are supposed to be getting into the game right now!) to obtain EXP potions or materials any faster than interlude drills. And interlude drills for new players have horribly bad efficiency.\n\nThis feels like a really big oversight. New players will literally be going into Arc 1 Chapter 4 right now with a bunch of Level 20 characters unless they're either soon given a free gift drop of awakener exp and materials or some kind of stamina-burning event is added.", "timestamp": "2026-05-20T19:21:10.096000+00:00", "thread_id": "1506738574861799474", "reactions": [{"emoji": "agree", "emoji_id": "1400771815076528258", "count": 6}]}
