{"id": "1506699104552747232", "channel_id": "1506699104552747232", "author_id": "800547495452999720", "author_name": "c3raphile", "content": "In traphase, Caecus’s exalt grants him 3 stacks of “Aberrant Blood”.  \nAberrant Blood should heal for 12 HP each, totalling 36 HP healed. \nHowever, this healing is unaffected by healing reduction such as “Deathmatch” and Blighten. \nFurthermore, this healing is strangely increased by far more than 50% with the Wheel of Destiny “By Rose Alone” (Increase Healing, Shielding and Damage of Exalt by 50%)", "timestamp": "2026-05-20T16:44:19.641000+00:00", "thread_id": "1506699104552747232", "attachments": [{"id": "1506699104984502272", "filename": "IMG_0698.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1239769, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1506699104552747232/1506699104984502272/IMG_0698.png?ex=6a0f3663&is=6a0de4e3&hm=d45fdddd5e7518cb874a37b6342242ffbf40181dc37666ecb43ec42684c41afe&"}, {"id": "1506699105446002788", "filename": "IMG_0699.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 972204, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1506699104552747232/1506699105446002788/IMG_0699.png?ex=6a0f3663&is=6a0de4e3&hm=ba7f89af3dc6dacbfe3bb997e4ccbcf60c806672beb7b21d9aa2e2fa523c8771&"}, {"id": "1506699106222084228", "filename": "IMG_0700.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1230723, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1506699104552747232/1506699106222084228/IMG_0700.png?ex=6a0f3664&is=6a0de4e4&hm=f96c310f05899fe9868625a8cfa68e636c8d692e405c3417622424576ea529f5&"}, {"id": "1506699106804830228", "filename": "IMG_0703.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1121404, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1506699104552747232/1506699106804830228/IMG_0703.png?ex=6a0f3664&is=6a0de4e4&hm=6a738f79b21e831c1fecb8da33d5dc1561740bc271cc352fec684aad9c574d93&"}, {"id": "1506699107253878985", "filename": "IMG_0704.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 971936, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachmen